    pol:annotatedText "the national statistics to be reported shall be as set out in the annexes. they shall be transmitted with the following frequencies: (a) annual, for the energy statistics in annex b; (b) monthly, for the energy statistics in annex c; (c) short-term monthly, for the energy statistics in annex d." ;
